<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c1">" مجهول، وقد ذكره ابن حبان في "</span>الضعفاء<span class="c1">". "</span>التلخيص<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(٢/ ٣٦٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
